"2\",\"coverUrl\":\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/profile/upload/2026/01/17/9c4d89ad238c65fa2f786a5f1ba20c12_20260117192230A002.jpg\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2026-01-17 18:39:45\",\"delFlag\":\"0\",\"description\":\"<p>123</p>\",\"endTime\":\"2026-01-18 00:00:00\",\"location\":\"\",\"maxParticipants\":3,\"params\":{},\"participantCount\":1,\"publishTime\":\"2026-01-17 18:39:45\",\"publishUserId\":1,\"publishUserName\":\"admin\",\"remark\":\"\",\"startTime\":\"2026-01-17 18:39:39\",\"status\":\"2\",\"summary\":\"\",\"title\":\"123123223\",\"updateBy\":\"teacher\",\"updateTime\":\"2026-01-18 00:09:01\",\"visiblePostIds\":\"\"}','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-18 00:09:00',90),(355,'成长故事',2,'com.ruoyi.web.controller.hx.HxStoryController.edit()','PUT',1,'teacher','管理员','/hx/story','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"ql-align-justify\\\"><strong class=\\\"ql-size-large\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">中秋的月光，平等地洒进每扇窗。</strong></p><p class=\\\"ql-align-justify\\\">\\t医护人员提着精心挑选月饼，轻轻放在每位患者手中，<span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">贴心叮嘱：“莲蓉馅不甜，长辈们吃着正好。”赵大爷接过月饼，没说话，只是望着月亮出神——那月光，大概也正照着他远方的儿女吧。护士搬来椅子，坐在他身边：“大爷，今晚我们陪您一起看月亮，这儿也是您的家。”</span></p><p class=\\\"ql-align-justify\\\"><span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">另一边，李阿姨正笑着打电话：“妈这儿也有月饼吃，豆沙的，等你回来我们再吃一次……”几句话，把整个病房都说暖了。这个夜晚，病痛暂时退居其次，人与人之间的靠近，成了最好的药。</span></p><p class=\\\"ql-align-justify\\\"><br></p><p class=\\\"ql-align-justify\\\">\\t<span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">重阳节前后，桂花开了，香气若有似无地飘进病房。医护人员端来刚蒸好的重阳糕，细心照顾着每位老人的不同需要——扶一把、吹一吹、陪一会儿。有老人吃着吃着就红了眼眶：“这味道，像我母亲从前做的……”</span></p><p class=\\\"ql-align-justify\\\"><strong class=\\\"ql-size-large\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\"><img src=\\\"/dev-api/profile/upload/2025/11/19/屏幕截图 2025-11-18 111108_20251119210438A001.png\\\"></strong></p><p class=\\\"ql-align-justify\\\">\\t<span style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">更让人动容的是做桂花画的时候。李爷爷手抖得厉害，却坚持要自己撒花瓣。当金色的桂花落在纸上，他笑得像个孩子：“这辈子第一次做这么风雅的事。”陈奶奶把完成的作品轻轻贴在胸前，闭眼闻着：“真香啊，跟我家院里那棵老桂花树一个味道。”那一刻，病房不再是病房，倒像是个老友相聚的温暖客厅。</span></p>\",\"coverUrl\":\"/profile/upload/2026/01/17/屏幕截图 2026-01-17 170458_20260117182208A004.png\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-11-14 15:27:54\",\"delFlag\":\"0\",\"likeCount\":1,\"params\":{},\"publishTime\":\"2025-11-14 15:35:52\",\"publishUserId\":1,\"publishUserName\":\"admin\",\"remark\":\"\",\"sort\":0,\"status\":\"1\",\"storyId\":1,\"summary\":\"太暖心了\",\"title\":\"暖心小故事1\",\"updateBy\":\"teacher\",\"updateTime\":\"2026-01-18 00:09:06\",\"viewCount\":146}','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-18 00:09:05',82),(356,'心灵树洞',2,'com.ruoyi.system.controller.HxTreeHoleController.edit()','PUT',1,'teacher','管理员','/system/hole','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"content\":\"你好，我不费劲，可以资助我1000块吗\",\"params\":{},\"status\":\"1\",\"treeHoleId\":6,\"userId\":101,\"userName\":\"230404106\"}','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-18 00:09:14',79),(357,'心灵树洞',2,'com.ruoyi.system.controller.HxTreeHoleController.edit()','PUT',1,'teacher','管理员','/system/hole','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"content\":\"你好，我不费劲，可以资助我1000块吗\",\"params\":{},\"status\":\"0\",\"treeHoleId\":6,\"userId\":101,\"userName\":\"230404106\"}','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-18 00:11:09',76),(358,'心灵树洞',2,'com.ruoyi.system.controller.HxTreeHoleController.edit()','PUT',1,'teacher','管理员','/system/hole','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"content\":\"你好，我不费劲，可以资助我1000块吗\",\"params\":{},\"status\":\"1\",\"treeHoleId\":6,\"userId\":101,\"userName\":\"230404106\"}','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-18 00:11:10',75),(359,'活动证明审核',2,'com.ruoyi.web.controller.hx.HxActivityController.auditParticipant()','POST',1,'teacher','管理员','/hx/activity/participant/10/audit','127.0.0.1','内网IP','10 {\"approved\":false,\"remark\":\"重新上传\"}','{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}',0,NULL,'2026-01-18 00:12:53',222),(360,'成长活动',2,'com.ruoyi.web.controller.hx.HxActivityController.edit()','PUT',1,'admin','管理员','/hx/activity','127.0.0.1','内网IP','{\"activityId\":10,\"actualStatu